@startuml
title URMA Connection Warmup - Worker Startup Sequence (PR #815)

header
<color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color> = 新增代码 | <color:#0066CC>**[EXISTING]**</color> = 已有代码
end header

skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFBCC
skinparam noteBorderColor #FF6B00

participant "WorkerN\n(Startup)" as WN
participant "EtcdCluster\nManager" as ECM
participant "ObjectCache\nClientWorkerSvc" as OCWS
participant "ObjectTable" as OT
participant "WorkerOcService\nGetImpl" as GET
participant "WorkerOC\nServer" as WOC
participant "EtcdStore" as ES
participant "Worker1..N\n(Peers)" as WP

== Phase 1: Worker Start (Pre-existing) ==

WN -[#0066CC]-> WOC : <color:#0066CC>**Start()**</color>
activate WOC
WN -[#0066CC]-> ECM : <color:#0066CC>**SetWorkerReady()**</color>
activate ECM
ECM -[#0066CC]-> ES : <color:#0066CC>**UpdateNodeState(ETCD_NODE_READY)**</color>
deactivate ECM

note right of ECM
  <color:#0066CC>**[EXISTING]**</color>
  此流程在 PR 前已存在
end note

== Phase 2: Local Warmup Object Preparation ==

WN -[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**MaybeStartConnectionWarmup()**</color>
activate WOC
note right of WOC
  <color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color>
  检查 warmup_connection 参数
  创建 warmupThreadPool_(4线程)
  创建 warmupControllerThread_
end note

WOC -[#FF6B00]-> OCWS : <color:#FF6B00>**PrepareUrmaWarmupObject()**</color>
activate OCWS
note right of OCWS
  <color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color>
  创建本地 1 字节预热对象
  同步执行，等待完成
end note

OCWS -[#0066CC]-> OT : ReserveGetAndLock()
activate OT
OT --[#0066CC]-> OCWS : entry locked
deactivate OT

OCWS -[#0066CC]-> OCWS : SetNewObjectEntry()
OCWS -[#0066CC]-> OCWS : SaveBinaryObjectToMemory()
note right of OCWS
  1 byte warmup value
end note
OCWS -[#0066CC]-> OT : Erase()
activate OT
OT --[#0066CC]-> OCWS : erased
deactivate OT
OCWS --[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**K_OK**</color>
deactivate OCWS

WOC -[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**Create warmupThreadPool_()**</color>
WOC -[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**warmupControllerThread_**</color>
deactivate WOC

== Phase 3: Readiness Probe ==

WN -[#0066CC]-> WOC : <color:#0066CC>**ReadinessProbe()**</color>
activate WOC
note right of WOC
  <color:#0066CC>**[EXISTING]**</color>
  此流程在 PR 前已存在
  K8s readiness probe 检查点
end note

WOC -[#0066CC]-> WOC : WaitForServiceReady()
WOC -[#0066CC]-> WOC : Write ready-check file
note right of WOC
  /health/ready
end note
deactivate WOC

== Phase 4: Async Peer Warmup (Background) ==

loop RunUrmaWarmupController() - every 1s until 30-110s
note over WOC
  <color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color>
  后台控制器：
  - 扫描 ETCD_CLUSTER_TABLE
  - 发现新 ready peer
  - 提交 warmup 任务到线程池
end note

    WOC -[#0066CC]-> ES : GetAll(ETCD_CLUSTER_TABLE)
    activate ES
    ES --[#0066CC]-> WOC : List<workerAddr>
    deactivate ES

    WOC -[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**ScheduleUrmaWarmupTasks()**</color>

    par for each new peer
        WOC -[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**warmupThreadPool_->Submit()**</color>
        note right of WOC
          lambda: WarmupUrmaConnectionToPeer()
        end note
        activate WOC
        WOC -[#FF6B00]-> GET : <color:#FF6B00>**WarmupGetObjectFromRemoteWorker()**</color>
        activate GET

        note right of GET
          <color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color>
          直接发起 remote get
          绕过 QueryMeta 流程
          超时 5s
        end note

        GET -[#0066CC]-> WP : RemoteGetRequest()
        activate WP

        alt URMA not connected yet
            WP -[#0066CC]-> WP : K_URMA_NEED_CONNECT
            WP -[#0066CC]-> WN : ExecOnceParrallelExchange()
            note right of WP
              <color:#0066CC>**[EXISTING]**</color>
              URMA 建链 handshake
            end note
        end

        WP --[#0066CC]-> GET : RemoteGetResponse
        GET -[#FF6B00]-> GET : <color:#FF6B00>**evictionManager_->Erase()**</color>
        GET -[#FF6B00]-> GET : <color:#FF6B00>**objectTable_->Erase()**</color>
        note right of GET
          <color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color>
          清理本地临时对象
        end note
        GET --[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**K_OK**</color>
        deactivate GET
        deactivate WP
        deactivate WOC
    end
end

== Phase 5: Warmup Completion ==

WOC -[#FF6B00]-> WOC : <color:#FF6B00>**GetUrmaWarmupSuccessCount()**</color>
note right of WOC
  <color:#FF6B00>**[NEW]**</color>
  打印日志：success_count/total_count
end note

legend right
  <color:#FF6B00>**■ NEW**</color> = 本 PR 新增的代码和函数
  <color:#0066CC>**■ EXISTING**</color> = PR 前已存在的代码路径
endlegend

@enduml